<lb ed="T" n="0892c26"/><persName key="A008831">釋慧演</persName>，姓<name>苗氏</name><ptr target="#n3596"/>，<placeName key="PL000000027119">襄陽</placeName>人也。父為<placeName key="PL000000021665">東平</placeName>紏曹。
<lb ed="T" n="0892c27"/><persName key="A008831">演</persName>幼入<placeName key="PL000000020573">開元寺</placeName><ptr target="#n3595"/>，聞經歡喜，求於<persName key="A013896">辯章<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>
<lb ed="T" n="0892c28"/>所度脫。<persName key="A013896">章</persName>日講《涅槃經》<ptr target="#n798"/>，<persName key="A008831">演</persName>常隨聽入神。既
<lb ed="T" n="0892c29"/>通深義，復能講談。一日結侶同遊<placeName key="PL000000043539">華</placeName>下<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2383"/>，思<pb ed="T" n="0893a" xml:id="T50.2061.0893a"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0893a01"/>登<placeName key="PL000000049236">毛女峯</placeName>，觀<placeName key="PL000000056421">仙掌</placeName>，路出<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛中</placeName>，乃參<persName key="A005612">荷澤<roleName>祖
<lb ed="T" n="0893a02"/>師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1144"/>，通達大觀。因入<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>，遂住<placeName key="PL000000029560">澧陽</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000000197">江南</placeName>得
<lb ed="T" n="0893a03"/>道者多矣。<date from-iso="+0796-02-18" key="j20118412012194" to-iso="+0797-02-05"><name>貞元</name>十二年</date>終<ptr target="#n3597"/>，享齡七十九云。</p>
